 service brands targeting the Canadian market.\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-5\" data-kid=\"38\">\n                    <button class=\"bg-cyan text-[#0B0C10] px-10 py-5 rounded-sm font-inter font-black text-lg uppercase tracking-wider hover:shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(102,252,241,0.7)] transition-all flex items-center gap-3 group relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"39\">\n                        <span class=\"relative z-10 flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"40\">\n                            Start Free Audit\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-arrow-right group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"41\"></i>\n                        </span>\n                        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-white/20 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300\" data-kid=\"42\"></div>\n                    </button>\n                    <button class=\"px-10 py-5 rounded-sm font-inter font-bold text-lg border border-white/20 hover:border-cyan hover:text-cyan transition-all flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"43\">\n                        View Live Feed\n                    </button>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"mt-16 flex items-center gap-8 border-t border-white/5 pt-10\" data-kid=\"44\">\n                    <div data-kid=\"45\">\n                        <div class=\"font-mono text-cyan text-2xl font-bold\" data-kid=\"46\">120+</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-[10px] uppercase text-[#C5C6C7] tracking-widest mt-1\" data-kid=\"47\">Active Accounts</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"w-px h-10 bg-white/10\" data-kid=\"48\"></div>\n                    <div data-kid=\"49\">\n                        <div class=\"font-mono text-cyan text-2xl font-bold\" data-kid=\"50\">CAD $12M</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-[10px] uppercase text-[#C5C6C7] tracking-widest mt-1\" data-kid=\"51\">Managed Spend</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"w-px h-10 bg-white/10\" data-kid=\"52\"></div>\n                    <div data-kid=\"53\">\n                        <div class=\"font-mono text-cyan text-2xl font-bold\" data-kid=\"54\">98.4%</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-[10px] uppercase text-[#C5C6C7] tracking-widest mt-1\" data-kid=\"55\">Retention Rate</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"relative flex justify-center items-center\" data-kid=\"56\">\n                <div class=\"relative w-[500px] h-[500px]\" data-kid=\"57\">\n                    \n                    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center z-10\" data-kid=\"58\">\n                        <video src=\"https://videos.pexels.com/video-files/34630451/14676799_640_360_30fps.mp4\" poster=\"https://images.pexels.com/videos/34630451/pexels-photo-34630451.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&fit=crop&h=630&w=1200\" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload=\"metadata\" class=\"w-[500px] h-[500px] object-cover rounded-full scale-110 opacity-70 mix-blend-screen\" data-kid=\"59\"></video>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    \n                    <div class=\"absolute -top-10 -right-4 z-20 glass-card p-5 rounded-xl animate-float shadow-2xl\" style=\"animation-delay: 0s\" data-kid=\"60\">\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\" data-kid=\"61\">\n                            <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan\" data-kid=\"62\">\n                                <i class=\"ti ti-chart-infographic\" data-kid=\"63\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <span class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#C5C6C7] uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"64\">Local Views</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"text-3xl font-black font-inter tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"65\">+340%</div>\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] text-cyan mt-1\" data-kid=\"66\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-trending-up\" data-kid=\"67\"></i>\n                            <span data-kid=\"68\">TORONTO REGION</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"absolute top-1/2 -left-20 z-20 glass-card p-5 rounded-xl animate-float shadow-2xl\" style=\"animation-delay: 2s\" data-kid=\"69\">\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\" data-kid=\"70\">\n                            <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan\" data-kid=\"71\">\n                                <i class=\"ti ti-target-arrow\" data-kid=\"72\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <span class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#C5C6C7] uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"73\">Conversion</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"text-3xl font-black font-inter tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"74\">CPL $18</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-[10px] text-[#C5C6C7] mt-1 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"75\">Meta Lead Flow</div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"absolute -bottom-12 right-10 z-20 glass-card p-5 rounded-xl animate-float shadow-2xl\" style=\"animation-delay: 4s\" data-kid=\"76\">\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\" data-kid=\"77\">\n                            <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan\" data-kid=\"78\">\n                                <i class=\"ti ti-map-2\" data-kid=\"79\"></i>\n                            </div>\n                            <span class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#C5C6C7] uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"80\">GMB Ranking</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"text-2xl font-black font-inter tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"81\">#1 Vancouver</div>\n                        <div class=\"w-full bg-white/5 h-1 rounded-full mt-3 overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"82\">\n                            <div class=\"h-full bg-cyan w-[95%]\" data-kid=\"83\"></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                \n                <div class=\"absolute w-[600px] h-[600px] border border-white/5 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"84\"></div>\n                <div class=\"absolute w-[800px] h-[800px] border border-white/5 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"85\"></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <section class=\"relative h-[900px] overflow-hidden flex items-center\" data-kid=\"86\">\n        \n        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-50\" data-kid=\"87\">\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544411047-c491e34a24e0?auto=format&w=1600&q=80&fit=crop\" alt=\"Toronto City Map\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale brightness-[0.4]\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"88\">\n        </div>\n        \n        \n        <div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[1200px] h-[1200px] pointer-events-none opacity-40\" data-kid=\"89\">\n            <div class=\"animate-radar absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 w-[2000px] h-[2000px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-[conic-gradient(from_0deg_at_50%_50%,transparent_0deg,rgba(102,252,241,0.2)_360deg)] rounded-full\" data-kid=\"90\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[300px] h-[300px] border border-cyan/20 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"91\"></div>\n            <div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] border border-cyan/20 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"92\"></div>\n            <div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[900px] h-[900px] border border-cyan/20 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"93\"></div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"container mx-auto px-10 relative z-10 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center\" data-kid=\"94\">\n            <div class=\"max-w-2xl\" data-kid=\"95\">\n                <div class=\"text-cyan font-mono text-sm tracking-[0.4em] mb-6 uppercase\" data-kid=\"96\">Local Grid Defense</div>\n                <h2 class=\"font-inter text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-[0.9]\" data-kid=\"97\">\n                    'NEAR ME' <br data-kid=\"98\"> DOMINANCE\n                </h2>\n                <p class=\"text-xl text-[#C5C6C7] mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-lg opacity-80\" data-kid=\"99\">\n                    Turn \"Near Me\" into \"Booked Now\". We automate your Google Business Profile to capture every local search in your service area, locking out competitors in real-time.\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6\" data-kid=\"100\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-5 glass-card rounded-xl group hover:border-cyan/40 transition-all cursor-default max-w-md tilt-3d\" data-kid=\"101\">\n                        <div class=\"p-3 bg-cyan/10 rounded-lg text-cyan\" data-kid=\"102\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-map-pin-filled text-2xl\" data-kid=\"103\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <div data-kid=\"104\">\n                            <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-1\" data-kid=\"105\">Grid Tracking v4.0</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-sm text-[#C5C6C7] opacity-70\" data-kid=\"106\">Monitor rankings point-by-point across your entire city with 500m precision.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-5 glass-card rounded-xl group hover:border-cyan/40 transition-all cursor-default max-w-md tilt-3d\" data-kid=\"107\">\n                        <div class=\"p-3 bg-cyan/10 rounded-lg text-cyan\" data-kid=\"108\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-message-2-share text-2xl\" data-kid=\"109\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <div data-kid=\"110\">\n                            <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-1\" data-kid=\"111\">Review Acceleration</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-sm text-[#C5C6C7] opacity-70\" data-kid=\"112\">Proprietary AI sequence to stack 5-star reviews and boost authority instantly.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"flex justify-center\" data-kid=\"113\">\n                <div class=\"bg-[#1F2833]/90 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-cyan/40 p-10 rounded-[2rem] w-[450px] shadow-[0_0_80px_rgba(102,252,241,0.25)] relative group tilt-3d-r tilt-3d\" data-kid=\"114\">\n                    \n                    <div class=\"absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 px-4 py-2 bg-cyan text-[#0B0C10] font-mono text-xs font-bold rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest shadow-lg\" data-kid=\"115\">\n                        You rank #1\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-10\" data-kid=\"116\">\n                        <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-cyan/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border border-cyan/20\" data-kid=\"117\">\n                            <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/game-icons-transparent@latest/svgs/lorc/radar-sweep.svg\" class=\"w-10 h-10\" style=\"filter: invert(86%) sepia(48%) saturate(336%) hue-rotate(125deg) brightness(101%) contrast(98%);\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"118\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"text-right\" data-kid=\"119\">\n                            <div class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-cyan uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\" data-kid=\"120\">Node Status</div>\n                            <div class=\"text-white font-bold\" data-kid=\"121\">Toronto - Downtown</div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"space-y-8\" data-kid=\"122\">\n                        <div data-kid=\"123\">\n                            <div class=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-mono mb-3\" data-kid=\"124\">\n                                <span class=\"text-[#C5C6C7]\" data-kid=\"125\">SEARCH VISIBILITY</span>\n                                <span class=\"text-cyan\" data-kid=\"126\">94%</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"h-2 bg-[#0B0C10] rounded-full overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"127\">\n                                <div class=\"h-full bg-cyan shadow-[0_0_10px_#66FCF1] w-[94%]\" data-kid=\"128\"></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        \n                        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\" data-kid=\"129\">\n                            <div class=\"bg-[#0B0C10] p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5\" data-kid=\"130\">\n                                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#C5C6C7] uppercase mb-1\" data-kid=\"131\">Clicks</div>\n                                <div class=\"text-xl font-black\" data-kid=\"132\">2,481</div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"bg-[#0B0C10] p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5\" data-kid=\"133\">\n                                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#C5C6C7] uppercase mb-1\" data-kid=\"134\">Actions</div>\n                                <div class=\"text-xl font-black\" data-kid=\"135\">154</div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div class=\"pt-6 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"136\">\n                            <div class=\"flex -space-x-3\" data-kid=\"137\">\n                                <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=1\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[#1F2833]\" alt=\"Avatar\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"138\">\n                                <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=2\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[#1F2833]\" alt=\"Avatar\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"139\">\n                                <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=3\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[#1F2833]\" alt=\"Avatar\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"140\">\n                                <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-cyan/20 border-2 border-[#1F2833] flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold text-cyan\" data-kid=\"141\">+12</div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#C5C6C7] leading-tight\" data-kid=\"142\">\n                                RECENT CONVERSIONS IN <br data-kid=\"143\"> <span class=\"text-white\" data-kid=\"144\">SCARBOROUGH, ON</span>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <section class=\"py-40 px-10 relative bg-[#0B0C10] overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"145\">\n        <div class=\"ambient-glow top-0 right-0\" data-kid=\"146\"></div>\n        <div class=\"container mx-auto relative z-10\" data-kid=\"147\">\n            <div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-end mb-28\" data-kid=\"148\">\n                <div data-kid=\"149\">\n                    <div class=\"text-cyan font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.5em] mb-6 uppercase\" data-kid=\"150\">Deployment Protocol</div>\n                    <h2 class=\"font-inter text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase leading-[0.9]\" data-kid=\"151\">From Recon <br data-kid=\"152\"> To <span class=\"text-cyan italic glow-cyan\" data-kid=\"153\">Takeover</span></h2>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"text-xl text-[#C5C6C7] opacity-70 leading-relaxed max-w-lg lg:justify-self-end\" data-kid=\"154\">\n                    A militarized 4-phase rollout. No vague retainers, no agency limbo — every week has a deliverable and a defined kill metric.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"relative\" data-kid=\"155\">\n                \n                <div class=\"hidden lg:block absolute top-[52px] left-[12.5%] right-[12.5%] h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan/0 via-cyan/50 to-cyan/0 shadow-[0_0_20px_#66FCF1]\" data-kid=\"156\"></div>\n                \n                <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10\" data-kid=\"157\">\n                    <div class=\"relative group tilt-3d\" data-kid=\"158\">\n                        <div class=\"w-[104px] h-[104px] rounded-2xl glass-card flex items-center justify-center mb-10 relative z-10 group-hover:border-cyan/50 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"159\">\n                            <span class=\"font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-cyan\" data-kid=\"160\">01</span>\n                            <span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-cyan/10 border border-cyan/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-cyan\" data-kid=\"161\"><i class=\"ti ti-radar-2 text-lg\" data-kid=\"162\"></i></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-inter text-2xl font-black mb-4 tracking-tight uppercase\" data-kid=\"163\">Audit & Recon</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-[#C5C6C7] opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-6\" data-kid=\"164\">Full teardown of your GMB, ad accounts, and competitor grid. We map every leak in your local funnel within 72 hours.</p>\n                        <div class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-cyan uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"165\">Week 0–1</div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"relative group tilt-3d\" data-kid=\"166\">\n                        <div class=\"w-[104px] h-[104px] rounded-2xl glass-card flex items-center justify-center mb-10 relative z-10 group-hover:border-cyan/50 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"167\">\n                            <span class=\"font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-cyan\" data-kid=\"168\">02</span>\n                            <span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-cyan/10 border border-cyan/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-cyan\" data-kid=\"169\"><i class=\"ti ti-settings-code text-lg\" data-kid=\"170\"></i></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-inter text-2xl font-black mb-4 tracking-tight uppercase\" data-kid=\"171\">System Build</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-[#C5C6C7] opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-6\" data-kid=\"172\">Landing pages, tracking, review automations, and campaign architecture assembled into one connected operating stack.</p>\n                        <div class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-cyan uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"173\">Week 1–2</div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"relative group tilt-3d\" data-kid=\"174\">\n                        <div class=\"w-[104px] h-[104px] rounded-2xl glass-card flex items-center justify-center mb-10 relative z-10 group-hover:border-cyan/50 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"175\">\n                            <span class=\"font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-cyan\" data-kid=\"176\">03</span>\n                            <span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-cyan/10 border border-cyan/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-cyan\" data-kid=\"177\"><i class=\"ti ti-rocket text-lg\" data-kid=\"178\"></i></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-inter text-2xl font-black mb-4 tracking-tight uppercase\" data-kid=\"179\">Launch Sprint</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-[#C5C6C7] opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-6\" data-kid=\"180\">A 30-day learning loop: 3+ ad angles live, GMB posting cadence active, and lead routing tested against real call volume.</p>\n                        <div class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-cyan uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"181\">Week 2–6</div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"relative group tilt-3d\" data-kid=\"182\">\n                        <div class=\"w-[104px] h-[104px] rounded-2xl glass-card flex items-center justify-center mb-10 relative z-10 group-hover:border-cyan/50 transition-colors border-cyan/40\" data-kid=\"183\">\n                            <span class=\"font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-cyan\" data-kid=\"184\">04</span>\n                            <span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-cyan border border-cyan rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#0B0C10]\" data-kid=\"185\"><i class=\"ti ti-shield-bolt text-lg\" data-kid=\"186\"></i></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-inter text-2xl font-black mb-4 tracking-tight uppercase\" data-kid=\"187\">Scale & Defend</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-[#C5C6C7] opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-6\" data-kid=\"188\">Winners get budget, losers get killed. Grid defense protocols keep competitors locked out while spend scales profitably.</p>\n                        <div class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-cyan uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"189\">Ongoing</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <section class=\"py-48 px-10 relative\" data-kid=\"190\">\n        <div class=\"ambient-glow bottom-0 right-0 opacity-40\" data-kid=\"191\"></div>\n        <div class=\"container mx-auto\" data-kid=\"192\">\n            <div class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-32\" data-kid=\"193\">\n                <div class=\"text-cyan font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.5em] mb-6 uppercase\" data-kid=\"194\">The Growth Stack</div>\n                <h2 class=\"font-inter text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tighter uppercase\" data-kid=\"195\">Engineered <br data-kid=\"196\"> For Scale</h2>\n                <p class=\"text-xl text-[#C5C6C7] opacity-70 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto\" data-kid=\"197\">Integrated acquisition systems that work in concert to build absolute market dominance for Canadian service brands.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-stretch\" data-kid=\"198\">\n                \n                <div class=\"bg-[#1F2833] p-12 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/5 hover:border-cyan/30 flex flex-col group shadow-2xl tilt-3d\" data-kid=\"199\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-10 text-cyan/60 group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors\" data-kid=\"200\">\n                        <i class=\"ti ti-brand-facebook text-7xl\" data-kid=\"201\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-inter text-3xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"202\">PAID SOCIAL ENGINE</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-[#C5C6C7] mb-10 leading-relaxed text-lg\" data-kid=\"203\">Hyper-targeted Meta Ads focusing on creative testing and automated lead routing for Canadian service brands.</p>\n                    <div class=\"mt-auto space-y-4 pt-10 border-t border-white/5\" data-kid=\"204\">\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-mono\" data-kid=\"205\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-checks text-cyan\" data-kid=\"206\"></i>\n                            <span class=\"text-[#C5C6C7]\" data-kid=\"207\">Dynamic Creative Optimization</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-mono\" data-kid=\"208\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-checks text-cyan\" data-kid=\"209\"></i>\n                            <span class=\"text-[#C5C6C7]\" data-kid=\"210\">24/7 Lead Hygiene Filter</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                \n                <div class=\"bg-[#1F2833] p-12 rounded-[2.5rem] border-2 border-cyan/40 scale-105 z-10 relative flex flex-col group shadow-[0_0_80px_rgba(102,252,241,0.15)] overflow-hidden tilt-3d\" data-kid=\"211\">\n                    \n                    <div class=\"absolute -top-16 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-48 opacity-20 pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-50 group-hover:scale-125 transition-all duration-700\" data-kid=\"212\">\n                        <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1677080865283-26f94ed332f1?auto=format&w=600&q=80&fit=crop\" alt=\"3D Pin\" class=\"w-full h-full object-contain rounded-full scale-110\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"213\">\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"mb-10 text-cyan\" data-kid=\"214\">\n                        <i class=\"ti ti-map-pin-2 text-7xl drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(102,252,241,0.6)]\" data-kid=\"215\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-cyan text-[#0B0C10] font-mono text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full mb-6 w-fit uppercase\" data-kid=\"216\">Most Requested</div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-inter text-3xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"217\">LOCAL SUPREMACY</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-[#C5C6C7] mb-10 leading-relaxed text-lg italic\" data-kid=\"218\">The gold standard for GMB management in the GTA and beyond. Automated ranking grid defense protocols.</p>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"bg-[#0B0C10] p-6 rounded-2xl border border-cyan/20 mb-10\" data-kid=\"219\">\n                        <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-4\" data-kid=\"220\">\n                            <span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-cyan\" data-kid=\"221\">PROTOCOL STATUS</span>\n                            <span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyan animate-pulse\" data-kid=\"222\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"text-sm font-mono text-white\" data-kid=\"223\">Active Ranking Grid: <span class=\"text-cyan\" data-kid=\"224\">LIVE</span></div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <button class=\"w-full py-5 bg-cyan text-[#0B0C10] font-black rounded-xl uppercase tracking-widest hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform shadow-xl\" data-kid=\"225\">Secure Your Territory</button>\n                </div>\n\n                \n                <div class=\"bg-[#1F2833] p-12 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/5 hover:border-cyan/30 flex flex-col group shadow-2xl tilt-3d tilt-3d-r\" data-kid=\"226\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-10 text-cyan/60 group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors\" data-kid=\"227\">\n                        <i class=\"ti ti-search text-7xl\" data-kid=\"228\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-inter text-3xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"229\">INTENT CAPTURE</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-[#C5C6C7] mb-10 leading-relaxed text-lg\" data-kid=\"230\">High-intent keyword harvesting paired with high-conversion local landing pages built to print appointments.</p>\n                    <div class=\"mt-auto space-y-4 pt-10 border-t border-white/5\" data-kid=\"231\">\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-mono\" data-kid=\"232\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-checks text-cyan\" data-kid=\"233\"></i>\n                            <span class=\"text-[#C5C6C7]\" data-kid=\"234\">Negative Term Scrubbing</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-mono\" data-kid=\"235\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-checks text-cyan\" data-kid=\"236\"></i>\n                            <span class=\"text-[#C5C6C7]\" data-kid=\"237\">24/7 Bid Management AI</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    \n        \n        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\" data-kid=\"238\">\n            <video src=\"https://videos.pexels.com/video-files/34633541/14679242_640_360_30fps.mp4\" poster=\"https://images.pexels.com/videos/34633541/pexels-photo-34633541.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&fit=crop&h=630&w=1200\" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload=\"metadata\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-[0.12] mix-blend-screen\" data-kid=\"239\"></video>\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0B0C10] via-transparent to-[#0B0C10]\" data-kid=\"240\"></div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n            <div class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-24\" data-kid=\"241\">\n                <div class=\"text-cyan font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.5em] mb-6 uppercase\" data-kid=\"242\">Sector Playbooks</div>\n                <h2 class=\"font-inter text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tighter uppercase\" data-kid=\"243\">Industries <br data-kid=\"244\"> We <span class=\"text-cyan italic\" data-kid=\"245\">Arm</span></h2>\n                <p class=\"text-xl text-[#C5C6C7] opacity-70 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"246\">Pre-built offer angles, booking flows, and ranking playbooks for Canada's highest-ticket local verticals.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\" data-kid=\"247\">\n                <div class=\"glass-card p-10 rounded-3xl group hover:border-cyan/50 cursor-default tilt-3d\" data-kid=\"248\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8\" data-kid=\"249\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan\" data-kid=\"250\"><i class=\"ti ti-tools text-3xl\" data-kid=\"251\"></i></div>\n                        <span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#C5C6C7] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:text-cyan transition-all\" data-kid=\"252\">PB-01</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-inter text-2xl font-black mb-3 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"253\">HVAC & Plumbing</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-[#C5C6C7] opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-6\" data-kid=\"254\">Emergency-intent capture with call-first campaigns and seasonal demand surges.</p>\n                    <div class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-cyan uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"255\">Avg CPL: $19–$32 CAD</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"glass-card p-10 rounded-3xl group hover:border-cyan/50 cursor-default tilt-3d\" data-kid=\"256\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8\" data-kid=\"257\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan\" data-kid=\"258\"><i class=\"ti ti-home-bolt text-3xl\" data-kid=\"259\"></i></div>\n                        <span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#C5C6C7] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:text-cyan transition-all\" data-kid=\"260\">PB-02</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-inter text-2xl font-black mb-3 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"261\">Roofing</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-[#C5C6C7] opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-6\" data-kid=\"262\">Storm-response funnels, financing offers, and brochure-to-WhatsApp handoffs.</p>\n                    <div class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-cyan uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"263\">Avg Ticket: $14K CAD</div>\n                </div>\n\n                </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8\" data-kid=\"264\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan\" data-kid=\"265\"><i class=\"ti ti-dental text-3xl\" data-kid=\"266\"></i></div>\n                        <span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#C5C6C7] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:text-cyan transition-all\" data-kid=\"267\">PB-03</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-inter text-2xl font-black mb-3 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"268\">Dental Clinics</h3>\n                    Implant and Invisalign offers with review velocity systems and recall automation.</div>",
